
<div class="card border border-2 border-primary my-5 mx-1">
	<div class="card-header text-center">
		<span class="badge bg-warning text-dark fs-3">Learning Hebrew</span>
	</div>

	<div class="card-body py-2">
		<div class="fs-5 fw-bold mb-0">Why Learn Hebrew?</div>
	</div>

	<div class="card-body py-1">
		<div class="card-title fx-6">There are several good reasons to learn a little Hebrew:</div>
	</div>
	
	<div class="card-body py-1">
		<ul class="fa-ul">
			<li><i class="fa-li fas fa-caret-right text-warning"></i>In your personal Bible study, knowing some of the Hebrew words from which the English words were translated can often lead to additional insights.</li>
			<li><i class="fa-li fas fa-caret-right text-warning"></i>Knowing a little Hebrew can be of great help if you ever travel to Israel.</li>
		</ul>
	</div>

