		<img class="img-fluid rounded" src="@Constants.Blobs.Link("Alephbet.jpg")" alt="Hebrew Alephbet" />
	</div>

</div>

<div class="card border border-2 border-primary my-3 mx-1">
	<div class="card-body">
		<h5>Consider this verse found in the New King Jame Version which reads</h5>
	</div>

	<div class="card-body">
		<p class="bg-primary-subtle fs-5 p-2 ms-3">
			<b>Zephaniah 3:9</b><br />
			<i class='fas fa-quote-left'></i>

			<sup class="text-primary fw-bold">9</sup>
			For then I will restore to the peoples a pure language, that they all may call on the name of the Lord, to serve Him with one accord.
		</p>
	</div>

	<div class="card-body">
		<h5>
			Do you suppose that the "pure language" might be Hebrew?<br />
			<a href="https://myhebrewbible.com/Hebrew/Zepc3v8"
				 class="btn btn-primary btn-sm float-end" target="_blank">
				<span class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></span> Learn More...
			</a>
		</h5>
	</div>

</div>

